| | $P |  $F |  $N | $E|
|      $M    |

probably create provider_hash keys such as THUMBGEN_P THUMBGEN_F THUMBGEN_N ...

this variables are useful for a bunch of reasons.
these seem to map to 
- Parent $P
- Folder $F
- Movie Name $N
- Extension $E
- Movie Path $M
